    <lb n="9"/>τ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ὰ</unclear> <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">νο</unclear>μι<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ζόμε</unclear>να ἔλαβαν ἀπ᾽ ἐμοῦ 

    <lb n="10"/>ἀλ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">λὰ</unclear> καὶ <choice><corr>προχρείαν</corr><sic>προχριαν</sic></choice>, καὶ <choice><corr>ἀλόγως</corr><sic>αλωκος</sic></choice> 

